description:
Check out some of our favorite shop products here: https://kgs.link/shop. Our shop is not only our most important source of income, but our passion project where we create sciencey products with of lot of love and detail.

Sources & further reading: https://sites.google.com/view/sources-three-ways-to-destroy/

The universe is going to die one day, and a fight between two titans will decide our cosmic fate.
On one side of this galactic battlefield, we have all the matter in the universe; on the other side, empty space infused with dark energy. Whoever wins will kill the universe in fun ways.
But who will that be?
We're looking at three possible ways to destroy the universe in our newest video.
